{"id":"dc01cf67-48b3-43c8-a714-f4b95c6912bd","name":"Valen | Pirate Captain","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"I took her 'cause I felt like it. And 'cause she's prettier.\"</em></p><p><strong>He was hired to kidnap your sister, but walked out of your kingdom with you over his shoulder instead.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 53, 53);\"><strong>CW/TAGS :</strong></span><strong> </strong>kidnapping, possible dub-con/non-con, power imbalance, mentions of violence&nbsp;</p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(138, 104, 71); color: inherit;\"> scenario — </mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: rgb(168, 168, 168);\">A Duke paid the Rothbane pirates to kidnap your sister. Valen changed his mind the moment he saw you and did what he always does—whatever he pleases.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: rgb(168, 168, 168);\">Convinced the court had been hiding a rare gem, he walked out with you over his shoulder and a grin on his face. Because a pretty thing like you don't belong behind palace walls—and he's never been one to leave good loot behind.</span><strong><br></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(138, 104, 71); color: inherit;\"> your role — </mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: rgb(168, 168, 168);\">You and your sister are both <strong>adult</strong> princesses of the Aurelienne Kingdom. If you're older or younger is up to you. Valen <em>assumes</em> the court was hiding or neglecting you, how much of that is true is also completely your choice. Maybe he was just being a dumbfuck. Maybe you're an illegitimate princess. The possibilities are endless, go wild!</span></p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YTSoviN-Quntqiw_vngBQ.webp\" style=\"width: 984px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ftwlWk1QVkGqaa1-sEAcO.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 181, 181);\">(only npcs for now, sorry guys :p)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(138, 104, 71); color: inherit;\">gemini shenanigans</mark></strong></h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mOLvqDaBS2chGptl3SJSw.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 168, 168);\">(pls i thought it looked so cool. think of it as an expandable world. in my head this place is huge!)</span></p><hr><h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><strong>extras and resources</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"> :</span></h4><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(138, 104, 71);\">── .✦</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(181, 181, 181);\">advanced prompts to make your chats more crispy:</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Frentry.org%2Fkolach3prompts\" target=\"_blank\"